-- SAP Sees ‘Good Growth Potential’ at Hana, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-03-09T06:19:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-09/sap-sees-good-growth-potential-at-hana-handelsblatt-reports.html
SAP AG (SAP) , which plans to double the
sales of its Hana unit in 2012 from last year’s 160 million
euros ($212 million), sees “good growth potential” at the
division in the following years as well,  Handelsblatt  reported
today, citing Jim Hagemann Snabe, the company’s co-chief
executive officer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
